lead_paragraph: The fifth week of the college football season offers arguably the best lineup of games since the opening weekend. With so many top 10 teams facing each other, this week could provide some clues on which teams have legitimate College Football Playoff aspirations.

headline.print_headline: Clemson-Louisville Highlights Trio of Top 10 Matchups
